  <header>
    <h1>Geotechnical Engineering Specialization</h1>
    <p>Master the fundamentals of soil mechanics, foundation design, and ground improvement with comprehensive learning resources.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="specialization-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Specialization Areas</h2>
    <div class="specialization-grid">
  
      <!-- Foundation Engineering -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-building-columns"></i>
          Foundation Engineering
        </div>
        <p>Focus on design and analysis of shallow and deep foundations for various soil conditions.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Shallow foundations</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Deep foundations</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Settlement analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/PracticalEngineering" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Practical Engineering</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/CivilEngineeringAcademy" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Civil Engineering Academy</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> GeoEngineer.org</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Soil Mechanics -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-mountain"></i>
          Soil Mechanics
        </div>
        <p>Study of soil behavior, properties, and classification for engineering applications.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Soil classification</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Shear strength</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Consolidation theory</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/@nptel" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> NPTEL Soil Mechanics</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/@TheGeotechnicalEngineer" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> The Geotechnical Engineer</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.issmge.org/education" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> ISSMGE Resources</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Geotechnical Earthquake Engineering -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-wave-square"></i>
          Geotechnical Earthquake Engineering
        </div>
        <p>Focus on soil behavior during earthquakes, liquefaction, and seismic design of foundations.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Soil liquefaction</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Seismic slope stability</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Ground response analysis</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/EERIvideos" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> EERI Learning</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/UCBerkeley" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> UC Berkeley Geotechnical Engineering</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.geerassociation.org/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> GEER Association</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- Projects section -->
  <section class="projects-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Industry Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-road"></i>
          Slope Stabilization
        </div>
        <p>Design and implement slope stabilization measures for highways and infrastructure.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Retaining Structures</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Soil Nailing</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Drainage Systems</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/engineering/geotech/pubs/nhi16072.pdf" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Research</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-water"></i>
          Ground Improvement
        </div>
        <p>Develop techniques to enhance soil properties for construction on problematic soils.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Soil Mixing</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Dynamic Compaction</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Grouting</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.dfi.org/publications/" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Resources</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-city"></i>
          Deep Excavation
        </div>
        <p>Design support systems for deep excavations in urban environments.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Diaphragm Walls</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Bracing Systems</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Dewatering</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/web-based-class-projects/select-topics-in-deep-excavation" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Guidelines</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Soil Classification</div>
        <p>Understand soil types, properties, and classification systems (USCS, AASHTO).</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/soil-mechanics" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Shear Strength</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of soil shear strength, testing methods, and failure criteria.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geotechdata.info/parameter/shear-strength.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Consolidation Theory</div>
        <p>Learn about soil settlement, time-dependent behavior, and consolidation testing.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/soil-mechanics/consolidation" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Slope Stability</div>
        <p>Study methods for analyzing and designing stable slopes in various soil conditions.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/slope-stability" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Retaining Structures</div>
        <p>Understand earth pressure theories and design of various retaining wall systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/earth-retaining-structures" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Foundation Design</div>
        <p>Learn about shallow and deep foundation systems, bearing capacity, and settlement analysis.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/foundation-engineering" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Soil Dynamics</div>
        <p>Study dynamic soil properties, wave propagation, and vibration analysis.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/soil-dynamics" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Ground Improvement</div>
        <p>Explore techniques for enhancing soil properties for construction purposes.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/ground-improvement" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Geosynthetics</div>
        <p>Master applications of geotextiles, geogrids, and geomembranes in geotechnical projects.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geosyntheticsociety.org/education" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Tunneling</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for underground excavation, support systems, and ground control.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.ita-aites.org/en/publications" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Geotechnical Investigation</div>
        <p>Study site investigation methods, in-situ testing, and soil sampling techniques.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/geotechnical-investigation" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Numerical Modeling</div>
        <p>Understand finite element analysis and numerical methods for geotechnical problems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/numerical-methods" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Unsaturated Soil Mechanics</div>
        <p>Explore behavior of partially saturated soils and their engineering applications.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.issmge.org/committees/technical-committees/fundamentals/unsaturated-soils" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Geoenvironmental Engineering</div>
        <p>Learn about contaminant transport, remediation, and waste containment systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/environmental-geotechnics" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Liquefaction</div>
        <p>Study soil liquefaction phenomena, assessment methods, and mitigation strategies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.geoengineer.org/education/soil-liquefaction" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

